name: Bill Max
description: I am what you call a Ladies man..Before you get any ideas.In this Contest it means That they like been around me.Which I think is because i make them feel comfortable.Just like anyone I like finer things of life.My friends tell me I’m funny on occasion,intelligent ,laid back,and confident.I like to have a good intellectual conversation. Other times I love to joke around.I think laughter is healthy.I love to watch comedy shows.I’m a good listener and I like to compromise and talk things out Overall,I’m easy going and I love all cultures in women. Sometimes I think women should be rulers of the earth.I work hard and I love to laugh and have a good time.I take pride in the way I look and I stay in shape.I love the outdoors,seeing live music shows, dining out, intelligent conversation, animals, a good bottle of wine, seeing a great movie.I am happy, healthy,funny,very romantic, very single, live alone.I love animals, and completely drug and disease free.I am well established in my carrier, goal oriented,and financially secure with a job I enjoy.
